Class HospitalPersonnel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.algonquinlive.college.java.silin.HospitalPersonnel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Doctor

    public class HospitalPersonnel
extends java.lang.Object
    In a hospital there are many people who work to ensure good health outcomes. Hospital personnel are paid salaries and such personnel could belong to different wards. An example of a ward is the inpatients ward, and inside the ward you can have specialties like Inpatients Theatre, etc.
